    • isEligibleToRegister

      public boolean isEligibleToRegister(String officerNric, String projectId)
      Checks if an officer is eligible to register for a specific project team. Rules: - Cannot have applied for the project as an Applicant. - Cannot be an approved Officer for another project during the same application period. This requires access to Project, Application, and Registration data. **Belongs in a Service layer.**
      Parameters:
      officerNric - The NRIC of the officer.
      projectId - The ID of the project to register for.
      Returns:
      true if eligible based on available data, false otherwise (full check needs service).

    • findByHandledProject

      public List<HdbOfficer> findByHandledProject(String projectId)
      Finds officers assigned to a specific project. Requires Project data access or a direct link in HdbOfficer model. **Belongs in Service Layer or requires model change.**
      Parameters:
      projectId - The ID of the project.
      Returns:
      List of officers handling the project.
